HEADWORD: Rememorate
<hw>Re*mem"o*rate</hw> <pr>(-?-r?t)</pr>, <pos>v. i.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>rememoratus</ets>, p. p. of <ets>rememorari</ets>. See
<er>Remember</er>.]</ety> <def>To recall something by means of memory;
to remember.</def> <mark>[Obs.]</mark> <rj><au>Bryskett.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

